### 3.7 CMD vs ENTRYPOINT

```dockerfile
# CMD — easily overridden
CMD ["node", "app.js"]

# ENTRYPOINT — fixed executable
ENTRYPOINT ["node", "app.js"]
CMD ["--port", "3000"]
```

```powershell
docker run myapp                    # runs entrypoint + default cmd
docker run myapp --port 4000        # entrypoint + override cmd args
```

